commit.message: Require 4.03 and drop result compatibility package.
OCaml 4.12 support: Rearrange types to support the new injectivity annotations in Map.S
Remove style.css and ad-hoc build script.
Remove funny characters in documentation spotted by Leo White (@lpw25).

Clarify the documentation of Fpath.normalize.

Thanks to Robert Atkey (@bobatkey) for reminding me not to
mislead the users of the library.
Fix test suite. Note test suite doesn't run on < 4.02.
Tweak dev build script and META file.
Fpath.of_string: use result instead of option.
